Make the most of your holidays and weekends to discover all those places you’ve always wanted. Get this American Tourister Backpack and pack your belongings for a perfect get away from your normal life. Designed for both men and women this backpack can be carried to short trips to the meadows or the countryside. The pattern of this bag is simple and matches the taste of the youth of today.

Body

Crafted from Polyester this backpack is resilient to common damages like abrasion and tearing. With dimensions of 310 x 430 x 240 mm this American Tourister Backpack has a slender profile but can fit in all your essentials like eatables water and other equipment.

Features

A well-equipped backpack makes your trip less stressful and helps you manage the load perfectly. If the bag is equipped with multiple features then it is a boon for the user. Equipped with three compartments this American Tourister Backpack allows you to arrange all your belongings in order of use and priority. In order to assure that your keys do not get misplaced this backpack has been furnished with a key holder. You can keep your water bottle and other small accessories in the side mesh pockets of this bag. In addition to these features this backpack has an organiser for pens visiting cards pendrive and CDs. If you are the kind of person who loves to listen to music on the move then this backpack is perfect for you as it has an earphone access. You can keep all your change in the zip pocket for coins. The zipper closure of this backpack keeps all your possessions safely encased within and prevents them from falling out.
